{
  "stem": "142.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well I-- most of my time, I still-- now that I'm retired, I still go and keep my acquaintances with the business I was in.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And two, three hours, from 12:00 to 3:00 in the afternoon, I always go to a-- I belong to a spa for many, many, many years.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I do exercise for 40 years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I try to have a quality life, not quantity.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first 10 years were-- were terrible nightmares, you know, practically daily or weekly, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my ex-wife was very good for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, she's-- she took care of me very-- very nicely.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But still from time to time-- and now, once we are talking, I was in  Poland about the 12th of October to the-- to the 20-- to the 19.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was in Poland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I went to Auschwitz and Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had 22-- the director of the Aish HaTorah from London-- he is the son of a good friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he asked me if I will accompany them, the 22, 24 people-- mostly girls and boys, 20 to 30 years old, from the University of London-- to-- they were-- they were wanting to have a lot of knowledge, and want to have somebody that was there, and especially that I was in the Sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went to all the camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we arrived Birkenau, I went to crematorium 2, which we destroy half of it when we were there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I found it exactly the same way, after 52 years.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Majdanek is intact, is just what it was before when-- when they started.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
